Class CubeExploreQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib.cube.CubeExploreQuery

public class CubeExploreQuery
extends Object
    Defines a query to perform exploration of the Cube data, e.g. to find dimension name and values and measure names.

        public CubeExploreQuery(long startTs,

        Creates instance of CubeExploreQuery that defines selection of data of Cube to explore in.
        Parameters:
        startTs - start time of the data selection, inclusive, in seconds since epoch
        endTs - end time of the data selection, exclusive, in seconds since epoch
        resolution - resolution of the aggregations explore
        dimensionValues - dimension name, dimension value pairs that define the data selection
